{"tid":1023934,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"想買將軍澳既樓，大家點睇？","createTime":"2019-02-16T07:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T17:45:45.000Z","uid":69010,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ed8bd43889e484efd76553c3eb4851a1c4946d3d","tid":1023934,"uid":69010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:17:54.000Z","msg":"依家係咪入市時機??<br />\n<br />\n住開將軍澳,可能食慣屎,覺得唔太差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想買日出康城果邊既樓,<br />\n<br />\n貪佢全部都係私樓,加上過幾年有將藍隧道<br />\n<br />\n交通唔係問題,本身有揸開車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但睇返近大半年既POST<br />\n<br />\n好多人都話將軍澳唔值咁貴,<br />\n<br />\n特別睇完下面呢張圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/keFb511.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkeFb511.png&h=d10b92a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一方面覺得應該冇咩可能會跌到咁低,一方面又覺得依家都仲係好貴<br />\n<br />\n所以想知大家對將來樓市係點睇?<br />\n<br />\n要跌幾多先叫合理?<br />\n<br />\n就結婚,怕入錯市....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a44facbe00ab8662f725f5dcb1f86a06616fbb","tid":1023934,"uid":193476,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:23:29.000Z","msg":"等多陣，2023先係入市時機。"},{"pid":"0ba3205ee7e1edd5ec3b86820c44e8ee41b60874","tid":1023934,"uid":69010,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b3a44facbe00ab8662f725f5dcb1f86a06616fbb","tid":1023934,"uid":193476,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:23:29.000Z","msg":"等多陣，2023先係入市時機。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:27:36.000Z","msg":"點解會係2023?<br />\n純粹好奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d2fc3c5db3a3048755b6fee80e0b5a669b7e95","tid":1023934,"uid":54761,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T07:28:30.